{{engname|《三五成群》|''Street Kids Violence''}}是一部於1999年出品的[[香港|香港]]犯罪劇情片，由[[錢昇瑋|錢昇瑋]]執導，内容改編自發生在1997年轟動全香港的[[秀茂坪童黨燒屍案|秀茂坪童黨燒屍案]]<ref>{{cite news|language = 中文|url = https://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/714889/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-%E7%95%B6%E5%B9%B4%E4%BB%8A%E6%97%A5-97%E5%B9%B4%E7%A7%80%E8%8C%82%E5%9D%AA%E7%AB%A5%E9%BB%A8%E7%87%92%E5%B1%8D%E6%A1%88-%E5%BE%8C%E6%94%B9%E7%B7%A8%E7%82%BA%E9%9B%BB%E5%BD%B1-%E4%B8%89%E4%BA%94%E6%88%90%E7%BE%A4|title = 97年秀茂坪童黨燒屍案 後改編為電影《三五成群》|publisher = 星島日報|accessdate = 2020-11-08|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200131081447/https://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/714889/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-%E7%95%B6%E5%B9%B4%E4%BB%8A%E6%97%A5-97%E5%B9%B4%E7%A7%80%E8%8C%82%E5%9D%AA%E7%AB%A5%E9%BB%A8%E7%87%92%E5%B1%8D%E6%A1%88-%E5%BE%8C%E6%94%B9%E7%B7%A8%E7%82%BA%E9%9B%BB%E5%BD%B1-%E4%B8%89%E4%BA%94%E6%88%90%E7%BE%A4|archive-date = 2020-01-31|dead-url = yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|language = 中文|url = http://newsbot.lib.cuhk.edu.hk/news/singpao/20001116/A08008.html|title = 童黨虐殺燒屍 年前哄動一時並搬上銀幕|publisher = 成報|date = 2000-11-16|accessdate = 2020-11-08|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201107232215/http://newsbot.lib.cuhk.edu.hk/news/singpao/20001116/A08008.html|archive-date = 2020-11-07|dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|language = 中文|url = http://newsbot.lib.cuhk.edu.hk/news/singtao/20001116/A13005.html|title = 電影記述童黨殺人|publisher = 星島日報|date = 2000-11-16|accessdate = 2020-11-08|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201107231923/http://newsbot.lib.cuhk.edu.hk/news/singtao/20001116/A13005.html|archive-date = 2020-11-07|dead-url = no}}</ref>。此電影在[[香港電影分級制度|香港電影分級制度]]中評為第III級，只准18歲或以上人士觀看，2017年6月10日在[[香港商業電台|香港商業電台]][[叱咤903|叱咤903]]舉行的「最港產電影節」再次上映<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://hk.ulifestyle.com.hk/activity/detail/108263/903%E6%A0%BC%E6%9C%80%E6%B8%AF%E7%94%A2%E9%9B%BB%E5%BD%B1%E7%AF%80-%E6%88%B2%E9%99%A2%E9%87%8D%E6%98%A08%E9%83%A8%E6%9C%AC%E5%9C%B0%E7%B6%93%E5%85%B8%E4%BD%9C