==反響及評價==
《三五成群》由上映到下畫約有港幣二十萬元票房收入，影評人[[石琪|石琪]]認為此電影是小本製作，沒有知名度高的演員，也沒有浪漫化包裝，劇情大致符合真實案情，具有現實感，眾演員都演得生動，能夠反映出當時的社會現實性，展現邊緣青少年欺善怕惡等不良狀況，惟他認為部份情節的表達手法不夠精緻，情理薄弱、具體實感不足，例如[[童黨|童黨]]經常在小童群益會服務單位門外鬧事，飾演「社工」的演員卻只是前來責罵一下，沒有進一步關注事件，情節令人難以信服<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.filmcritics.org.hk/film-review/node/2016/03/14/%E4%B8%89%E4%BA%94%E6%88%90%E7%BE%A4%EF%BC%9A%E4%BB%A3%E8%A1%A8%E6%80%A7 |title = 三五成群：代表性 |date = 1999 |publisher = 香港影評庫 |author = 石琪 |language = 中文 |accessdate = 2020-11-08 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190906042328/https://www.filmcritics.org.hk/film-review/node/2016/03/14/%E4%B8%89%E4%BA%94%E6%88%90%E7%BE%A4%EF%BC%9A%E4%BB%A3%E8%A1%A8%E6%80%A7 |archive-date = 2019-09-06 |dead-url = no }}</ref>。有評論則認為此電影改編自真人真事，劇情發展在觀眾意料之內，不能有太多新意，且只著重描寫童黨的行為，缺乏較為深層的心理描寫<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.cinespot.com/hkmreviews/%E4%B8%89%E4%BA%94%E6%88%90%E7%BE%A4 |title = 三五成群 |publisher = 動映地帶 |language = 中文 |accessdate = 2020-11-08 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200809174232/https://www.cinespot.com/hkmreviews/%E4%B8%89%E4%BA%94%E6%88%90%E7%BE%A4 |archive-date = 2020-08-09 |dead-url = no }}</ref>，電影其後在互聯網流傳，引起關注，部份對白成為網民的[[流行語|流行語]]<ref>{{cite news|language =中文|author =林勉一|url =https://www.thestandnews.com/society/2018%E5%B9%B4%E7%9C%8B1999%E5%B9%B4%E7%9A%84%E5%BB%BF%E5%85%AB%E5%BA%A7%E5%A4%A7%E7%8E%8B/|title =2018 年看 1999 年的廿八座大王|publisher =立場新聞|date =2018-02-22|access-date =2020-11-08|archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20190815043227/https://www.thestandnews.com/society/2018%E5%B9%B4%E7%9C%8B1999%E5%B9%B4%E7%9A%84%E5%BB%BF%E5%85%AB%E5%BA%A7%E5%A4%A7%E7%8E%8B/|archive-date =2019-08-15|dead-url =no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|language =中文|author =陳穎思|url =https://www.hk01.com/%E9%9B%BB%E5%BD%B1/336415/%E4%B8%89%E4%BA%94%E6%88%90%E7%BE%A420%E5%91%A8%E5%B9%B4-%E4%B8%8A%E6%98%A0%E9%9A%94%E5%8D%81%E5%B9%B4%E6%89%8D%E7%88%86%E7%B4%85-%E7%A5%9E%E4%BB%99b-%E5%B0%8D%E7%99%BD%E6%88%90%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%E7%B6%93%E5%85%B8|title =三五成群20周年 上映隔十年才爆紅 「神仙B」對白成網民經典|publisher =香港01|date =2019-06-03|access-date =2020-11-08|archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20201108025901/https://www.hk01.com/%E9%9B%BB%E5%BD%B1/336415/%E4%B8%89%E4%BA%94%E6%88%90%E7%BE%A420%E5%91%A8%E5%B9%B4-%E4%B8%8A%E6%98%A0%E9%9A%94%E5%8D%81%E5%B9%B4%E6%89%8D%E7%88%86%E7%B4%85-%E7%A5%9E%E4%BB%99b-%E5%B0%8D%E7%99%BD%E6%88%90%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%E7%B6%93%E5%85%B8|archive-date =2020-11-08|dead-url =no}}</ref>。

